From 54bc080afd2632cc5a7df605806c03e0296b4858 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Cursor Agent <cursoragent@cursor.com>
Date: Thu, 9 Jul 2026 15:46:51 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Implement realtime lead pickup alerts with Web Push and
 in-app overlay

- Add service worker for RealtimeLead and RealtimeLeadTaken push handling
- Show full-screen pickup alert with sound when a realtime lead arrives
- Call pickup API and dismiss notifications when lead is taken by anyone
- Show one-time daily limit warning when consultant cannot pick up more leads
- Register Web Push on consultant go-online and from dashboard settings
- Wire GetDashboardStatus API for online eligibility block reasons
